Vision & MissionLeadershipLocationsSonaca Group 


About Us | Locations

 


Across the U.S. and around the world, LMI is a leader in providing aerostructures, systems and components to the aerospace industry. For more than 68 years, we have provided solutions to our customers’ most challenging problems across the entire aircraft lifecycle, from design and build to manufacture and overhaul. Our integrated approach ensures that our customers receive the highest quality products, best customer service, and the most outstanding value in the industry.

Established in 1948
Approximately 2,000 employees
21 locations within the United States, Mexico, the United Kingdom and Sri Lanka
More than 1,000,000 sq. ft. of manufacturing space
AS9100 certified
NADCAP approved

