Capabilities

 


LMI is uniquely positioned to provide you with higher quality, more cost-effective aerospace structures, systems and components. Unlike other providers, our capabilities span the entire lifecycle of an aircraft, from design build to manufacture and overhaul. This breadth of engineering and manufacturing expertise, combined with our integrated approach, enables us to deliver superior products faster than the competition. Since 1948, we have partnered with a variety of aerospace manufacturers, and we have what it takes to help your business soar to new heights. 








