LMI Aerospace, Inc. provides design engineering services, structural assemblies, kits, and components to the aerospace, defense, and technology markets primarily in the United States.
The IT department for LMI Aerospace has recently been integrated across several units, and is now responsible for change management and program management offices for the company's Aerostructures and Engineering Services segments, as well as internal IT.

Several teams within the… MoreThe IT department for LMI Aerospace has recently been integrated across several units, and is now responsible for change management and program management offices for the company's Aerostructures and Engineering Services segments, as well as internal IT.

Several teams within the department are primarily dedicated to security and internal IT systems, as well as enterprise-wide technical support. Other internal teams are responsible for internal and client-facing IT application support and development. 

An additional group focuses on implementing automation solutions for the company's payroll and AP/AR department.





